        <div id="tempo" class="col s12">
          <div class="col s12">
            <h3>Tempo</h3>
            <p>Tempo markings show how fast or slow music should be played</p>
            <p>Some of the basic tempo markings are:</p>

            <ul class="collapsible expandable white">
              <li>
                <div class="collapsible-header"><i class="material-icons">arrow_drop_down</i>Accelerando</div>
                <div class="collapsible-body"><span>Gradually getting quicker, can be written as accel.</span></div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <div class="collapsible-header"><i class="material-icons">arrow_drop_down</i>Adagio</div>
                <div class="collapsible-body"><span>Slow</span></div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <div class="collapsible-header"><i class="material-icons">arrow_drop_down</i>Allegretto</div>
                <div class="collapsible-body"><span>Fairly quick</span></div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <div class="collapsible-header"><i class="material-icons">arrow_drop_down</i>Allegro</div>
                <div class="collapsible-body"><span>Quick</span></div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <div class="collapsible-header"><i class="material-icons">arrow_drop_down</i>Andante</div>
                <div class="collapsible-body"><span>Medium speed</span></div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <div class="collapsible-header"><i class="material-icons">arrow_drop_down</i>Rallentando</div>
                <div class="collapsible-body"><span>Gradually getting slower, can be written as rall.</span></div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <div class="collapsible-header"><i class="material-icons">arrow_drop_down</i>Ritardando</div>
                <div class="collapsible-body">
                  <span>Gradually getting slower (similar to Rallentando)<p>Can be written as either ritard. or rit.</p></span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <div class="collapsible-header"><i class="material-icons">arrow_drop_down</i>Ritenuto</div>
                <div class="collapsible-body"><span>Immediately slower<p>Can be written as either riten. or rit.</p></span></div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="dynamics" class="col s12">
          <div class="col s10">
